.subckt fir_cla Vdd Xnew_0 Xnew_1 Xnew_2 Xnew_3 Xnew_4 Xnew_5 Xold_0 Xold_1 Xold_2 Xold_3 Xold_4 Xold_5 phi0_0 phi0_1 phi0_2 phi0_3 phi0_4 phi0_5 phi1_0 phi1_1 phi1_2 phi1_3 phi1_4 phi1_5 phi2_0 phi2_1 phi2_2 phi2_3 phi2_4 phi2_5 phi3_0 phi3_1 phi3_2 phi3_3 phi3_4 phi3_5
